overview: Felix plans to spend the weekend at a music festival in Amsterdam with his buddy, Kai. Meanwhile, his girlfriend, Emmi, ought to stay home and grade papers. But commitment is not exactly Kai‘s strongest suit, and then Emmi‘s high school friend, Magda, turns up with some intriguing revelations. Naturally, things get a little out of hand—and everybody is naked in the end!
tagline: A refreshingly up-to-date, sun-dappled homage to 1970s porn
title: Rock Paper Scissors
